{"tid":41488,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉兆佳：中央不會讓香港變成顛覆基地","createTime":"2016-12-16T02:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T02:50:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03e0b434dbaa0d332036bc7fe824cf9f03362c83","tid":41488,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳出席電台節目時表示，特首梁振英宣布不競逐連任並非意料之外的事，又說如梁振英強行尋求連任或令香港出現更大反彈，建制派繼續分裂，使鬥爭更激烈。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳表示，中央對於涉及重大國家利益的事情，是不會讓特區政府自行處理。他又認為政改是國家層面的事，不會讓香港變成顛覆國家的基地。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳又認為，香港是不會有類似西方的真普選，又指中央難以開放特首選舉，因會令結果難以控制。他又表示，不會支持任何候選人，因未有最適合的人選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1302683-20161216.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1302683-20161216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZP7SNDWUMIiicflaSKQl3hpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=041e7ac3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1302683-20161216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=70072860\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1302683-20161216.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"27241fa66ab8be34d077d2326499f3ef8467569f","tid":41488,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T02:50:24.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾學棍成日係度扮智者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}